  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span> <span>2025-09-19 18:41</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">北京</span></p>\n  <p>RL 长训练再不崩了。</p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=75971bb5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW9kZtsN2DxYcqcK6v8OHXApmvRg31cSl7hVjeJa8bJnvu6Otp8Dxfq49mJRSxHB6d3XRY41UjtoEA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-wrap: wrap; caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px; color: rgb(163, 163, 163) !important;\" mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" class=\"js_darkmode__0\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;color: rgb(163, 163, 163) !important;\">\n   <div mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;\">\n    <div mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__2\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;\">\n     <div data-id=\"85660\" data-custom=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\" data-color=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\" mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: currentcolor; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__3\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: currentcolor;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;\">\n      <div data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 2em; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-right-style: none; border-left-style: none; text-decoration: inherit; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\" mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" class=\"js_darkmode__4\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 2em 0px 0px;padding: 0.5em 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);border-top: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;border-right-style: none;border-left-style: none;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;\">\n       <p mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"29.75\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: -1.2em; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; text-align: center; font-family: inherit; border-width: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: currentcolor; visibility: visible; line-height: 29.75px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__5\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;text-align: center;font-family: inherit;border-width: initial;border-style: initial;border-color: currentcolor;visibility: visible;line-height: 29.75px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span mp-original-font-size=\"15\" mp-original-line-height=\"29.75\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: inherit;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(117, 117, 118);text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;line-height: 29.75px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">机器之心发布</span></span></p>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: center;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.6em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 12px;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">机器之心编辑部</span></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">“MoE+Long-CoT（长思维链）+RL（强化学习）” 这条技术路线存在难以兼顾训练稳定性和效果的难题。9 月 19 日，蚂蚁百灵大模型团队把 “难啃的骨头” 直接做成开源礼包 ——Ring-flash-2.0。100B 总参、6.1B 激活，数学 AIME25 拿下 86.98 分，CodeForces elo 分数 90.23，128K 上下文实测 200+token/s。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">更关键的是，他们通过独创的棒冰（icepop）算法和长周期的 RL 训练，Ring-flash-2.0 在多项推理榜单上（数学、代码和逻辑推理）取得了显著突破，性能达到了 40B 以内 dense 模型的 SOTA 水平，甚至可与参数量更大的 MoE 模型相媲美。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503508062\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5111111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c99997bc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9kZtsN2DxYcqcK6v8OHXAptg1G8BjOXaib0F3AmaGFk9cqscwqLiaV9ibvBXBeAibpQmEk6OxmEKt7ww%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503508065\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5148148148148148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b0d7d22f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9kZtsN2DxYcqcK6v8OHXApc6R2XibNicXdqsdQ9YkYMaZh1iarWhPxvoODml9LaScmPWO0O4stIMX9g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">Ring-flash-2.0 性能表现</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">机器之心深度拆解，这一开源项目，为什么可能改写下一阶段大模型的竞争节奏。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">一、从 “不能用” 到 “敢开源”：MoE 长思考的临界点</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2025 年，业内流行一张 “死亡曲线”：在长思维链场景下，MoE 模型 RL 训练存在奖励崩溃的问题。于是大家只能把学习率调小、任务提前终止，无法继续训练。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">棒冰（icepop）算法：让 RL 进行长周期的稳定训练</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Ring-flash-2.0 的破冰点在于 “棒冰（icepop）”：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">双向截断 + 掩码修正</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，一句话总结 ——“把训推精度差异过大的 token 当场冻住，不让它回传梯度”。 &nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">最终，icepop&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">能够保持稳定的强化学习训练过程</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，避免了 GRPO 出现的训练崩溃问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503508067\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.3096590909090909\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1056\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=41f890cc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9kZtsN2DxYcqcK6v8OHXApTZIXUkgMxgWkyI2lv3ZROxm4YsvlvibVkLzzNguW702W1m4ia8xOqOibA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">左图为 GRPO 训练到 180-200 步开始崩溃，icepop 能实现持续稳定提升； 右图为 GRPO 训练不久出现梯度爆炸，icepop 能持续稳定在合理范围。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">与 GRPO 相比，icepop 还将训推精度差异约束在合理范围内，显示出对于</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">控制训推精度差异有效性</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"503508068\" data-ratio=\"0.3089430894308943\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"984\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3156a267&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9kZtsN2DxYcqcK6v8OHXApMnH1MAo376LdlkeAIfD63icmRfHvRGHaTuBp30weXc5qkSE0KiamU3Iw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">左图为 GRPO 训推精度差异随着训练成指数上升，icepop 较为平稳；右图为训推精度差异最大值，GRPO 随着训练上升非常明显，icepop 维持在较低水位。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">效果肉眼可见：训练再也不崩，百灵团队内部笑称，“终于不用担心训练无法长跑的问题”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(123, 12, 0);\">详细的棒冰（icepop）算法介绍参考技术博客：<a href=\"https://ringtech.notion.site/icepop\" target=\"_blank\">https://ringtech.notion.site/icepop</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Two-staged RL：先 “算对”，再 “像人”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">百灵大模型团队首先采用 Long-CoT SFT，采用包含数学、代码、逻辑和科学四大领域为主体的多学科高质量推理数据集，让模型 “学会思考”；第二步，通过可验证奖励的 RLVR（Reinforcement Learning with Verifiable Rewards），把推理逼到极限；随后，加入 RLHF，用高质量人类偏好数据，把格式、安全、可读性拉回舒适区。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503508070\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.4666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1020\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fce99b13&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9kZtsN2DxYcqcK6v8OHXApuwTUJABogUMDL0HV8eKuz9x2YYfTsR0mQk0Pd9iaXia3Yaicnoo43NX5w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">百灵团队验证了直接融合 RLVR+RLHF 的联合训练和 Two-staged RL，两种方式在实验中效果差异不大。 但由于 RLVR 和 RLHF 的问题难度不一致，RLHF 的思维链长度相对较短，放在一起训练会有较多等待长尾现象，从工程效率角度，使用了 Two-staged RL 方案。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">二、6.1B 激活打平 40B Dense，成本曲线出现 “拐点”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">大模型竞争进入 “第二幕”，核心指标不再是 “谁参数多”，而是 “谁性价比高”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"503508071\" data-ratio=\"0.8905472636815921\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1005\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=460dd4d5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9kZtsN2DxYcqcK6v8OHXApAO89lnzZribpyXBx4ibrnK7bz3BnOccqESxUO0xlld2MU5tLg9HuDqog%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">Ring-flash-2.0 架构图。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">继承 Ling 2.0 系列的高效 MoE 设计，通过&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">1/32 专家激活比、MTP 层等架构优化</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，Ring-flash-2.0 仅激活 6.1B (non-embedding 4.8B) 参数，即可等效撬动约 40B dense 模型的性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">得益于小激活、高稀疏度的设计，Ring-flash-2.0 在 4 张 H20 部署下实现&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">200+ token/s 的吞吐</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，大幅降低高并发场景下 Thinking 模型的推理成本。同时，Ring-flash 借助 YaRN 外推可支持&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">128K 长上下文</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，随着输出长度的增加，其相对加速比最高可达 7 倍以上。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">生成速度对比</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">竞赛数学视频</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">贪吃蛇case</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">arcprize case</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">冒泡排序可视化</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503508120\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7093596059113301\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1015\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a95e448f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FKmXPKA19gW9kZtsN2DxYcqcK6v8OHXApIArLZN4aAhUfx2rM4bYxHoeog6YHWRWUH9IeSsdd3yDRqKBvH8x3Jw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">粒子烟花模拟</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">生成搜索引擎首页 query：请仿照 Perplexity，设计并生成一个搜索引擎首页，网站名称为 “想搜”，slogan 为 “想搜，才会赢”。请实现基本的搜索界面、风格化 Banner 和搜索输入区。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">生成搜索引擎首页</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">结语：大模型竞争进入 “高性价比” 时代</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">从 2022 年 ChatGPT 点燃生成式 AI，到 2024 年长思考成为新战场，行业一直在等一个 “既聪明又便宜” 的推理模型。Ring-flash-2.0 用 100B 总参、6.1B 激活、200+token/s 的速度，把「Long-CoT + RL」做到工程可落地，还顺手把训练稳定性、推理成本、开源生态一次性打包。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如果说 GPT-4 开启了 “大模型可用时代”，那 Ring-flash-2.0 或许正式拉开了 “MoE 长思考高性价比时代” 的帷幕。剩下的问题只有一个：你准备用它做什么？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">开源地址：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(123, 12, 0);\">HuggingFace：<a href=\"https://huggingface.co/inclusionAI/Ring-flash-2.0\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/inclusionAI/Ring-flash-2.0</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(123, 12, 0);\">ModelScope：<a href=\"https://modelscope.cn/models/inclusionAI/Ring-flash-2.0\" target=\"_blank\">https://modelscope.cn/models/inclusionAI/Ring-flash-2.0</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(123, 12, 0);\">GitHub： <a href=\"https://github.com/inclusionAI/Ring-V2\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/inclusionAI/Ring-V2</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(123, 12, 0);\">技术博客： <a href=\"https://ringtech.notion.site/icepop\" target=\"_blank\">https://ringtech.notion.site/icepop</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin: 5px 8px 0px;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">© THE END&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 5px 8px 0px;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">转载请联系本公众号获得授权</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 5px 8px 0px;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">投稿或寻求报道：liyazhou@jiqizhixin.com</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"10000\"></mp-style-type></p>\n  <p><a href=\"2650991769\">阅读原文</a></p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/link-proxy/?k=2249aeba&amp;r=1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%3F__biz%3DMzA3MzI4MjgzMw%3D%3D%26mid%3D2650991769%26idx%3D2%26sn%3De346c7e90433162637ccc7d268e5ad5d\">跳转微信打开</a></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "蚂蚁百灵团队开源 Ring-flash-2.0 大模型，通过独创 icepop 算法解决 MoE+长 CoT+RL 训练稳定性难题，实现高性价比推理。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "蚂蚁百灵团队开源 Ring-flash-2.0 大模型，通过独创 icepop 算法解决 MoE+长 CoT+RL 训练稳定性难题，实现高性价比推理。",
  "summary": "文章介绍了蚂蚁百灵团队开源的 Ring-flash-2.0 大模型，旨在解决 MoE、长思维链（Long-CoT）与强化学习（RL）结合时训练稳定性差、易崩溃的难题。该模型总参 100B，激活参数仅 6.1B，通过独创的“棒冰（icepop）”算法（双向截断+掩码修正）实现了 RL 长周期的稳定训练，避免了梯度爆炸。Ring-flash-2.0 采用 Two-staged RL 训练方案，并结合高效 MoE 设计，在数学、代码和逻辑推理等多项榜单上取得 SOTA 性能，可与 40B 以内的 dense 模型媲美，且显著降低了推理成本，支持 128K 长上下文，标志着大模型竞争进入“高性价比”时代。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "独创“棒冰（icepop）”算法解决了 MoE 模型 RL 长周期训练的稳定性问题。",
      "explanation": "该算法通过双向截断和掩码修正，有效控制训推精度差异，避免了梯度爆炸和训练崩溃，使 RL 训练能够持续稳定提升，是实现 Long-CoT+RL 工程落地的关键。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Ring-flash-2.0 以小激活参数实现大模型性能，大幅降低推理成本。",
      "explanation": "仅激活 6.1B 参数即可达到 40B dense 模型的性能，得益于高效 MoE 设计，其高稀疏度特性显著提升了高并发场景下的推理吞吐量，实现“既聪明又便宜”。"
    },
    {
      "point": "采用 Two-staged RL 训练策略，兼顾模型推理能力与人类偏好。",
      "explanation": "先通过 Long-CoT SFT 和 RLVR 让模型“算对”和“推理到极限”，再通过 RLHF 优化格式、安全性和可读性，确保模型在性能和用户体验上达到平衡。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "\"MoE+Long-CoT（长思维链）+RL（强化学习）\" 这条技术路线存在难以兼顾训练稳定性和效果的难题。",
    "Ring-flash-2.0 的破冰点在于 \"棒冰（icepop）\"：双向截断 + 掩码修正，一句话总结 ------\"把训推精度差异过大的 token 当场冻住，不让它回传梯度\"。",
    "百灵大模型团队首先采用 Long-CoT SFT，采用包含数学、代码、逻辑和科学四大领域为主体的多学科高质量推理数据集，让模型 \"学会思考\"；第二步，通过可验证奖励的 RLVR（Reinforcement Learning with Verifiable Rewards），把推理逼到极限；随后，加入 RLHF，用高质量人类偏好数据，把格式、安全、可读性拉回舒适区。",
    "大模型竞争进入 \"第二幕\"，核心指标不再是 \"谁参数多\"，而是 \"谁性价比高\"。",
    "如果说 GPT-4 开启了 \"大模型可用时代\"，那 Ring-flash-2.0 或许正式拉开了 \"MoE 长思考高性价比时代\" 的帷幕。"
  ],
